adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.blink_dagger_main=The fabled dagger used by the fastest assassin ever to walk the lands
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.blink_dagger_help_l1=Use <Sneak> + click to blink towards target location

adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.butterfly_main=Only the mightiest and most experienced of warriors can wield the Butterfly, but it provides incredible dexterity in combat
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.butterfly_help_l1=Use <Sprint> + click to activate flutter to gain increased attack and movement speed

adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.ethereal_blade_main=A flickering blade of a ghastly nature, it is capable of dealing damage in both magical and physical planes
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.ethereal_blade_help_l1=Use <Sneak> + click to place a remnant of yourself in the magical plane (only you will see this)
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.ethereal_blade_help_l2=Use <Sneak> + click  again to materialize yourself again at your ghost's location
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.ethereal_blade_help_l3=You will also materialize from your ghost when this effect expires

adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.hurricane_pike_main=A legendary pike once held as royal sigil of the ancient wyvern riders
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.hurricane_pike_help_l1=Use <Sneak> + click to push your target forward
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.hurricane_pike_help_l2=Use <Sprint> + click to push yourself forward

adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.scythe_of_vyse_main=The most guarded relic among the cult of Vyse, it is the most coveted weapon among magi.
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.scythe_of_vyse_help_l1=Use <Sneak> + click to hex the target entity and turn them into a pig
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.scythe_of_vyse_help_l2=Pigs are useless and can not do anything but wander around and squeal helplessly
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.scythe_of_vyse_help_l3=Squael piggy, squeal

adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.manta_style_main=An axe made of reflective materials that causes confusion amongst enemy ranks
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.manta_style_help_l1=Should be dual wielded for full effect
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.manta_style_help_l2=Use <Sneak> + click to create an illusion for each manta style
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.manta_style_help_l3=Use <Sprint> + click to swap with target illusion of yourself

adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.mjollnir_main=Thor's magical hammer, made for him by the dwarves Brok and Eitri
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.mjollnir_help_l1=Use <Sneak> + click to invoke lightning

adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.shadow_blade_main=The blade of a fallen king, it allows you to move unseen and strike from the shadows
adventurers_artifacts.tooltip.shadow_blade_help_l1=Use <Sneak> + click to become fully invisible, interacting with the world will break invisibility


